{"tid":1663876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩服裝公司停止購入新疆棉花","createTime":"2019-10-19T16:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T04:22:21.000Z","uid":225818,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9005887de132f9e3098f261742cd02bdc3812c36","tid":1663876,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"澳洲兩間服裝品牌以擔憂侵犯人權為由停止採購新疆棉花<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，兩間澳洲服裝公司 Cotton On 及 Target Australia 已停止由中國新疆採購棉花原材料。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司電視節目《Four Corners》於七月揭露，有新疆維吾爾族穆斯林被當局拘留並被強迫在當地紡織工廠工作。此後，Cotton On 集團目前已完成針對其供應鏈的內部檢討。<br />\n<br />\n節目又透露，Target Australia 當時已開始就由新疆採購棉花原材料的做法進行內部檢討；同時，Jeanswest、Dangerfield、Ikea、H&amp;M 等品牌亦被披露有從新疆採購棉花原材料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國已將新疆當地的拘留設施稱為「集中營」。中國當局聲稱，設立有關「再教育營」，目的為將被拘留者「去極端化」並向他們教授新技能。<br />\n<br />\nCotton On 是由一間位於新疆的外判商 Litai Textiles 購入棉花。該公司證實，Cotton On 一名員工去年到訪了 Litai Textiles 一間位於「再教育營」僅六公里以外的紡織廠。<br />\n<br />\nCotton On 表示，將不會再繼續向 Litai Textiles 採購棉花原材料，並將「絕對致力確保產品供應鏈合乎道德」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，Target Australia 在進行一項針對新疆 Huafu 公司工廠所供應原材料的內部調查後，目前已「決定停止由該工廠訂購產品」。<br />\n<br />\n國際品牌 H&amp;M 亦有與 Huafu 合作，但強調 Huafu 公司提供的紗線來自新疆以外的工廠。該公司向《Four Corners》表示，曾經要求參觀 Huafu 公司位於新疆的廠房，調查後「未有發現強迫勞工的跡象」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource :<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/target-cotton-on-drop-suppliers-after-four-corners-investigation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Ftarget-cotton-on-drop-suppliers-after-four-corners-investigation&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoOrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=de88e6e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/target-cotton-on-drop-suppliers-after-four-corners-investigation</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">買衫要識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5dc0f599733384a033695ab223865276d040e3be","tid":1663876,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f7b1257fd91c97acfdc98101d4432c5372f5f1","tid":1663876,"uid":11454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQZLyA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQZLyA7.png&h=6555082e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMUJI<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b6096643ff32e0ecc73a139e52a749dc561318","tid":1663876,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3e4ea9602d9e18a136c40f136bf91988e25f85","tid":1663876,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"收到, 去幫襯COTTON ON"},{"pid":"003e2f86fee768b6e91ff843f23df3a783e90289","tid":1663876,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f7b1257fd91c97acfdc98101d4432c5372f5f1","tid":1663876,"uid":11454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQZLyA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQZLyA7.png&h=6555082e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMUJI<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"咁都比巴打搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買日貨就買u記啦<br />\nu記而家多左好多products係made in 東南亞"}]}